  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The prevalence of malnutrition in patients with colorectal cancer is recorded. We want to
      find out, if a malnourished patient has more complications after the elective surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All patients attending elective colorectal surgery are screened for malnutrition in advance.
      Their length of stay in the hospital and the complications are recorded.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
